description: Da Burger Shack is a Chicago-inspired burger truck bringing some good eats to the Miami streets. Burger Shack masterminds, the Hernandez brothers, show their Chi-town origins in these delicious burgers and fries, but draw on their time in Miami to make sure these great dishes pack a punch. Each bite you take carries years of burger-making expertise. Don't miss out on this fabulous experience!
name: Da Burger Shack
